elias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/05\/supplication-two-phrases-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":17531,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Two phrases are easy, highly rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo words are beloved to the Most Merciful. They are light on the tongue but heavy on the scale: Glory and praise to Allah, and glory to Allah the Almighty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7563, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2694 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26883,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/05\/four-powerful-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":17531,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Four powerful supplications for morning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Juwayriah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to her one morning for the dawn prayer and she was in the mosque. Then, he returned later in the morning while she was sitting. The Prophet said, \u201cYou have not left this position you are in.\u201d She\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20188,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/20\/dua-hamd-trees-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":17531,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Trees